'''Amazon Luna'''是一个由[[亞馬遜公司|Amazon]]开发和运营的[[云游戏|云游戏]]平台。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Amazon announces new cloud gaming service called Luna|url=https://www.theverge.com/2020/9/24/21451371/amazon-luna-cloud-gaming-service-twitch-alexa-controller|accessdate=2020-12-10|date=2020-09-24|last=Webster|first=Andrew|work=The Verge|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924181803/https://www.theverge.com/2020/9/24/21451371/amazon-luna-cloud-gaming-service-twitch-alexa-controller|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Amazon's Luna cloud gaming service arrives next month|url=https://www.engadget.com/amazon-cloud-game-streaming-luna-reveal-173946193.html|accessdate=2020-12-10|work=Engadget|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107173602/https://www.engadget.com/amazon-cloud-game-streaming-luna-reveal-173946193.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Amazon Luna: What we know about the new cloud gaming service|url=https://www.cnet.com/news/amazon-luna-what-we-know-about-the-new-cloud-gaming-service/|accessdate=2020-12-10|last=Blumenthal|first=Eli|work=CNET|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118095328/https://www.cnet.com/news/amazon-luna-what-we-know-about-the-new-cloud-gaming-service/|dead-url=no}}</ref> Luna于2020年9月24日宣布，用户可自2020年10月20日开始通过邀请来获得抢先体验资格。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Amazon Luna release date, game list, and controller for the Stadia-killer|url=https://www.inverse.com/gaming/amazon-luna-release-date-game-list-controller-early-access|accessdate=2020-12-10|last=Franzese|first=Tomas|work=Inverse|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030105543/https://www.inverse.com/gaming/amazon-luna-release-date-game-list-controller-early-access|dead-url=no}}</ref> Amazon Luna将推出多达100种不同的游戏，<ref>{{Cite web|title=A closer look at Luna, Amazon's cloud gaming service|url=https://www.engadget.com/luna-amazon-cloud-gaming-interview-pwa-apple-173948922.html|accessdate=2020-12-10|work=Engadget|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924183230/https://www.engadget.com/luna-amazon-cloud-gaming-interview-pwa-apple-173948922.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 价格为每月5.99美元，并提供来自[[亚马逊云计算服务|AWS]]的支持。Luna将与[[Twitch|Twitch]]进行集成，并在[[个人电脑|PC]]、[[MacOS|Mac]]、[[Amazon_Fire_TV|Amazon Fire TV]]、[[iOS|iOS]]（作为[[渐进式网络应用程序|渐进式网络应用程序]]）以及不久后的[[Android|Android]]平台上发行。Amazon与[[育碧|Ubisoft]]合作创建了一个Luna专用的游戏频道，这将使Luna的订阅者在游戏发布当天即可访问Ubisoft。截至2020年11月，Ubisoft+(Beta) 频道的每月额外订阅费用为14.99美元。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Amazon Partners With Ubisoft On A Luna Game-Streaming Channel|url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/amazon-partners-with-ubisoft-on-a-luna-game-streaming-channel/1100-6482563/?UniqueID=89844952-FE93-11EA-9755-36C496E8478F&ServiceType=twitter&PostType=link&ftag=ftag=GSS-05-10aab8e&TheTime=2020-09-24T18:27:00|accessdate=2020-12-10|work=GameSpot|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216155918/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/amazon-partners-with-ubisoft-on-a-luna-game-streaming-channel/1100-6482563/?UniqueID=89844952-FE93-11EA-9755-36C496E8478F&ServiceType=twitter&PostType=link&ftag=ftag%3DGSS-05-10aab8e&TheTime=2020-09-24T18%3A27%3A00|dead-url=no}}</ref>

Luna的抢先体验目前仅适用于在美国境内订阅的用户，国际版发行期尚未确定。

这是作为Amazon与其它云游戏平台（如[[Google_Stadia|Stadia]]、[[Xbox_Game_Pass|Xbox Game Pass]]、[[PlayStation_Now|PlayStation Now]]和[[GeForce_Now|GeForce Now]]）竞争而推出的产品。

